OL,4,CSchool protests force U-turn after sick
OL,5,Cpupil banned from wearing cap
OL,6, A teenager with a rare illness that has
OL,7, caused her hair to fall out is now able
OL,8, to wear a cap to school after teachers
OL,9, initially denied her request.
OL,11,FElla Goodwin's father said the
OL,12,F13-year-old was told a cap or hoodie
OL,13,Fwas not part of the uniform policy at
OL,14,FHeritage High School in Clowne,
OL,15,FDerbyshire.
OL,17,FThe row led to a protest outside the
OL,18,Fschool involving dozens of pupils on
OL,19,FMonday morning.
